data.title: Salman Khan, Shah Rukh Khan share screen space in 'Pathaan'; Fans leaked scenes from the movie
data.meta_description: Within a few hours of Pathaan's release, despite multiple requests from the 'Pathaan' team, Internet users prominently revealed key elements of the film on social media in which Salman Khan and Shah Rukh Khan are sharing the screen.
data.text:
Synopsis

Within a few hours of Pathaan's release, despite multiple requests from the 'Pathaan' team, Internet users prominently revealed key elements of the film on social media in which Salman Khan and Shah Rukh Khan are sharing the screen.

Despite multiple requests from the 'Pathaan' team, Internet users have prominently leaked key elements of the film on social media. Excited fans could not resist sharing Salman Khan's extended cameo in the film.

Shah Rukh Khan starrer 'Pathaan'began with a thunderous response from the First Day First Show (FDFS). As fans flocked to the theatres, one of the actor's pivotal moments was even leaked.

Tiger (Salman Khan) and Kabir (Hrithik Roshan from War) join 'Pathaan' in defending the land from enemies. Salman makes his Pathaan debut as Tiger in an action-packed 10-minute sequence. The scene has already been teased, and fans are hailing it as the "best scene" in the film.

"TIGER literally owns #Pathaan in the entire scene and @iamsrk couldn't help but see him brutally eclipse him in the movie," one user wrote after leaking the scenes as photos. Another user leaked some 'Pathaan' images and stated that Pathaan delivered on its promises. “Huge blockbuster. Thank you very much, Sid Anand!,” he added.

According to recent reports, several websites, including Tamilrockers, Filmyme4wap, Filmyzilla, Mp4movies, Pagalworld, and Vegamovies, leaked Shah Rukh Khan's Pathaan online before its official release. If this is true and the film is leaked online, Shah Rukh Khan's comeback film could suffer massive losses, potentially amounting to millions of rupees.

'Pathaan', starring Shah Rukh Khan, has been released, and the entire Bollywood industry is overjoyed. Apart from Shah Rukh, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham also played a key role in the film, which was released on January 25, 2023.

FAQs

Q1. Who is the writer of 'Pathaan'?

Siddharth Anand and Shridhar Raghavan.

Q2. What is the budget of Pathaan?

Rs 250 crores.
